      • convertAndCastAttributeValueListToArray

        public static <T> T[] convertAndCastAttributeValueListToArray(com.sun.tools.javac.util.List<com.sun.tools.javac.code.Attribute> annotatedValues,
                                                              Class<T> type)
        Converts an Attribute List to an array of passed type.
        Type Parameters:
        T - generic Type
        Parameters:
        annotatedValues - The list to convert
        type - The arrays target type
        Returns:
        an array of passed type containing all casted elements of passed annotatedValues list or null if passed annotatedValues are null.
        Throws:
        ClassCastException - will be thrown if Attributes of List cannot be cast to passed type
